## Anti-Patterns (AVOID)

| Pattern | Problem | Correction |
|---------|---------|------------|
| Vague titles | Not informative | "Results" -> "Clinical validation of iMEX in pancreatic cancer" |
| Missing statistics | Incomplete | Always include n, error type, P-values |
| Inconsistent panel labeling | Confusing | Use lowercase `(a)`, `(b)` consistently |
| Undefined abbreviations | Unclear | Define on first use in caption |
| Missing scale bars | Incomplete | All micrographs need scale information |

